documentation:
Given the path/name and value pairs in the items list, build a dict
with all config values represented by items.

Example:

```
given items=[("a.b.c","1"), ("a.e.f","2")]
return {
    "a": {
        "b": {
            "c": "1"
        }
        "e": {
            "f": "2"
        }
    }
}
```
